{"tid":1922684,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★調查指近四成初創企業因肺炎疫情裁員","createTime":"2020-03-12T16:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T04:29:52.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7493f7044eeefdf07777b7d5270d82c18941d28b","tid":1922684,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:50:03.000Z","msg":"有初創組織調查發現，受肺炎疫情影響，超過70%初創企業業務下跌超過50%，近40%的初創企業亦已經裁員，當中以娛樂及教育行業佔比最多，另外45%初創企業亦考慮裁員。受訪初創企業當中，全數認為政府支援不足，97%初創企業對本港營商環境不樂觀，有20%初創企業選擇離開香港市場，70%企業則需要開拓海外市場，其中最多企業選擇台灣，其次為東南亞及日韓市場。<br />\n<br />\n調查訪問218間初創企業，其中涵蓋專業或顧問、教育、美容美髮、零售及飲食等行業。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.999351/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.999351%2F2&d=xKwzLSQbN%2FgnQ4qVdIYE%2BKZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=8d4f482f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.999351/2</a>"},{"pid":"81f33478e3f79f9fffed3764b95383b95ec35382","tid":1922684,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39100b835bcc9acff0abf8bf9393c2128b330f3a","tid":1922684,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T04:29:52.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}